  "id" : "api/common/PlatformLocation",
  "title" : "PlatformLocation",
  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"platformlocation\">PlatformLocation</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label class\">class</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/common\">@angular/common</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation\" class=\"code-anchor\">PlatformLocation</a> } from <a href=\"api/common\">'@angular/common'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/common/src/location/platform_location.ts#L10-L48\">common/src/location/platform_location.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  <section class=\"class-overview\">\n<h2 id=\"overview\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3ivgu86loww6mg4fq1brezlnd\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>概览</h2>\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\nclass <a href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation\" class=\"code-anchor\">PlatformLocation</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation#getBaseHrefFromDOM\">getBaseHrefFromDOM(): string</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation#onPopState\">onPopState(fn: LocationChangeListener): void</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation#onHashChange\">onHashChange(fn: LocationChangeListener): void</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation#pathname\">get pathname: string</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation#search\">get search: string</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation#hash\">get hash: string</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation#replaceState\">replaceState(state: any, title: string, url: string): void</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation#pushState\">pushState(state: any, title: string, url: string): void</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation#forward\">forward(): void</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation#back\">back(): void</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8gmvjxo2nxome2qghrsv41d08\">此类不应由应用程序开发人员直接使用。请使用 \n<a href=\"api/common/Location\"><code>Location</code></a>。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"a02vqevgbxsha3qyb9qirz6fo\"><code><a href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation\" class=\"code-anchor\">PlatformLocation</a></code> 封装了对 DOM API 的所有调用，这使得路由器可以与平台无关。 这意味着我们可以为 Angular 支持的不同平台提供 \n<code><a href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation\" class=\"code-anchor\">PlatformLocation</a></code> 的不同实现。例如，\n<code>@angular/platform-browser</code> 提供了特定于浏览器环境的实现，而 \n<code>@angular/platform-webworker</code> 提供了适合与 Web Worker 一起使用的实现。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"30hex41cv9bdybt78z8by6y6m\"><code><a href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation\" class=\"code-anchor\">PlatformLocation</a></code> 类被所有 \n<a href=\"api/common/LocationStrategy\"><code>LocationStrategy</code></a> 实现直接使用，当它们需要与 DOM API（如 pushState、popState 等）交互时。</p>\n<a href=\"api/common/LocationStrategy\"><code>LocationStrategy</code></a>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"es9bhbcl714ne6o8r9q1ab4s1\">反过来被 \n<a href=\"api/common/Location\"><code>Location</code></a> 服务使用，该服务被 \n<a href=\"api/router/Router\"><code>Router</code></a> 直接使用，以便在路由之间导航。由于 \n<a href=\"api/router/Router\"><code>Router</code></a> / \n<a href=\"api/common/Location\"><code>Location</code></a> / \n<a href=\"api/common/LocationStrategy\"><code>LocationStrategy</code></a> 与 DOM API 之间的所有交互都通过 \n<code><a href=\"api/common/PlatformLocation\" class=\"code-anchor\">PlatformLocation</a></code> 类进行，因此它们都是与平台无关的。</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"instance-members\">\n  <h2 id=\"members\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e62kgm2ztk7rgk6auybfiv91o\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>成员</h2>\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"getBaseHrefFromDOM\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">getBaseHrefFromDOM(): string</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"onPopState\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">onPopState(fn: <a href=\"api/common/LocationChangeListener\" class=\"code-anchor\">LocationChangeListener</a>): void</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"onHashChange\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">onHashChange(fn: <a href=\"api/common/LocationChangeListener\" class=\"code-anchor\">LocationChangeListener</a>): void</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"pathname\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">get pathname: string</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"search\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">get search: string</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"hash\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">get hash: string</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"replaceState\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">replaceState(<a href=\"api/animations/state\" class=\"code-anchor\">state</a>: any, title: string, url: string): void</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"pushState\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">pushState(<a href=\"api/animations/state\" class=\"code-anchor\">state</a>: any, title: string, url: string): void</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"forward\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">forward(): void</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    <hr class=\"hr-margin\">\n  \n    <div class=\"instance-member\">\n  <a id=\"back\"></a>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">back(): void</code-example></div>\n\n    \n    \n  \n</section>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/HashLocationStrategy\n - api/common/PathLocationStrategy\n - api/platform-webworker/WORKER_APP_LOCATION_PROVIDERS\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/animations/state\n - api/common\n - api/common/Location\n - api/common/LocationChangeListener\n - api/common/LocationStrategy\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#back\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#description\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#forward\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#getBaseHrefFromDOM\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#hash\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#members\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#onHashChange\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#onPopState\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#overview\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#pathname\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#platformlocation\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#pushState\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#replaceState\n - api/common/PlatformLocation#search\n - api/router/Router\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/common/src/location/platform_location.ts#L10-L48\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/common\n-->"
